[
  {
    "key": "e84c0b41e6bcdd4d629123185a5043dd8369cd4a082cf8931b42a71f6364ad2c",
    "original": ", who commands the greatest reward of life: the fear of one's own enemies! Look, if I lather a little and catch the light, the muscles gleam. Would it not be that the heavens were mistakened for above, when all the women say they find them right here, particularly here, upon my glorious pecs?}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{%fullname% is not the best warrior here, let's be clear. Captain, look at my muscles, is it not I, \" + bros[0].getName() + \", who commands the greatest reward of life: the fear of one's own enemies! Look, if I lather a little and catch the light, the muscles gleam. Would it not be that the heavens were mistakened for above, when all the women say they find them right here, particularly here, upon my glorious pecs?}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c03c4acb0798e6ec3c9ea6f95d32f28c08156323916808af49719efb93cbb753",
    "original": ", who commands the ladies of this realm. Need not ask me how. Behold! Look at it! Look at the size of it! Yeah. That's what I thought. Fools, train all you want, you can't have this!}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{%fullname% thinks muscles make for glory. Wrong. Captain, it is I, \" + bros[2].getName() + \", who commands the ladies of this realm. Need not ask me how. Behold! Look at it! Look at the size of it! Yeah. That's what I thought. Fools, train all you want, you can't have this!}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c64afd5a578f04bfc3c48c20f778e5a0c3ad50a2fab95edc53d1b6c12908b70b",
    "original": ", who is your greatest gladiator. I am the one who swept the legs of a lindwurm and choked it out with its own tail! What you bastards say? You call that a tall tale? Pah! 'Tis a horizontal lizard at best.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{Why are you looking at %fullname%? Captain, it is I, \" + bros[1].getName() + \", who is your greatest gladiator. I am the one who swept the legs of a lindwurm and choked it out with its own tail! What you bastards say? You call that a tall tale? Pah! 'Tis a horizontal lizard at best.}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "74fa2035f42f1ad4819853da3cdaf38fe85bf4247c77d2a7474c5e64aff2adc3",
    "original": "Eager to prove himself outside the arena",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "5ddbe8d7f07eda3b47f43f0dee0cf820362f5ea2260a73de9be49277d0769000",
    "original": "Gladiators",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Gladiators\""
  },
  {
    "key": "eb162448f6b6d824b3155cc1badfbf8b1e4cace6c0d50bf8e821df750da6b212",
    "original": "[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_155.png[/img][/p][p]You've fought in the arenas of the south for years. First for your freedom, then for crowns, and finally to become immortal. What else does fate have in stock for you?\n\n[color=#bcad8c]Gladiators:[/color] Start with three experienced gladiators with good equipment, but very high daily wages.\n[color=#bcad8c]Legends of the Arena:[/color] Each gladiator has a unique trait in combat.\n[color=#bcad8c]Glorious Three:[/color] You can never have more than 12 men in your roster, and if all of your three starting men should die, your campaign ends.[/p]",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"[p=c][img]gfx/ui/events/event_155.png[/img][/p][p]You've fought in the arenas of the south for years. First for your freedom, then for crowns, and finally to become immortal. What else does fate have in stock for you?\\n\\n[color=#bcad8c]Gladiators:[/color] Start with three experienced gladiators with good equipment, but very high daily wages.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Legends of the Arena:[/color] Each gladiator has a unique trait in combat.\\n[color=#bcad8c]Glorious Three:[/color] You can never have more than 12 men in your roster, and if all of your three starting men should die, your campaign ends.[/p]\""
  },
  {
    "key": "652ef632b7830436b7629ec16705b592d00b7c7592d90801526e4498d3bdf05a",
    "original": "the Bear",
