  {
    "key": "e5223477abdf8872768ae63c81c6c446c8810a8fe0611e215ff9fd3bb03a6d71",
    "original": "{%fullname% is not the best warrior here, let's be clear. Captain, look at my muscles, is it not I, ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{%fullname% is not the best warrior here, let's be clear. Captain, look at my muscles, is it not I, \" + bros[0].getName() + \", who commands the greatest reward of life: the fear of one's own enemies! Look, if I lather a little and catch the light, the muscles gleam. Would it not be that the heavens were mistakened for above, when all the women say they find them right here, particularly here, upon my glorious pecs?}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "af7e316267658f76a500ec3be72e114c7d9698d423303b2ffb5c4cd92f1bd425",
    "original": "{%fullname% is somber about the passing of a good friend, but he looks to the future knowing that he has someone behind him at all times. Behind him in a brotherly way, that is. And spiritually. Brotherly and spiritually, only.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bro.getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"{%fullname% is somber about the passing of a good friend, but he looks to the future knowing that he has someone behind him at all times. Behind him in a brotherly way, that is. And spiritually. Brotherly and spiritually, only.}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e9593bba99b11c734f22d78e02b4de6ac842fe9ff3e8fd4eacf3f2d697f5eeb5",
    "original": "{%fullname% thinks muscles make for glory. Wrong. Captain, it is I, ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{%fullname% thinks muscles make for glory. Wrong. Captain, it is I, \" + bros[2].getName() + \", who commands the ladies of this realm. Need not ask me how. Behold! Look at it! Look at the size of it! Yeah. That's what I thought. Fools, train all you want, you can't have this!}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e992d0ce5f21cc3eb8b6e7d325088c6529c36bffa725e1650e366441fea04f1a",
    "original": "{Why are you looking at %fullname%? Captain, it is I, ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"{Why are you looking at %fullname%? Captain, it is I, \" + bros[1].getName() + \", who is your greatest gladiator. I am the one who swept the legs of a lindwurm and choked it out with its own tail! What you bastards say? You call that a tall tale? Pah! 'Tis a horizontal lizard at best.}\""
  },
  {
    "key": "9c04835ac444bee7fc1f9174bde6f90bd9941cf4555d7e806f060c76650f96a3",
    "original": "{You should know something, captain. I'm glad you stay out of the fray. I haven't felt this alive in what must be ten years. And if you see me out there about to go down, you stay right where you are, because I'll be right where I want to be.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "bro.getBackground().m.RawDescription = \"{You should know something, captain. I'm glad you stay out of the fray. I haven't felt this alive in what must be ten years. And if you see me out there about to go down, you stay right where you are, because I'll be right where I want to be.}\""
  }
]